    <h2 id="why-zinc">Why Zinc Gummies Are Essential for Immune and Skin Health</h2>

    <p>Zinc is a trace mineral that functions as a cofactor in over 300 enzymatic reactions in the human body, including immune cell development, protein synthesis, DNA repair, and cell division. It is particularly critical for the adaptive immune system — without adequate zinc, T-cells cannot mature properly, natural killer cell activity declines, and antibody production is impaired. This makes zinc one of the most functionally important micronutrients for immune defense.</p>

