    </div>

    <p>The gummy format has made zinc supplementation more accessible, particularly for individuals who experience nausea with zinc tablets — a common complaint due to zinc's GI-irritating properties in certain forms. The form of zinc in a gummy determines both its absorption efficiency and its likelihood of causing stomach discomfort, making this the most important factor in product selection.</p>

